page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI's latest fine-tuning capabilities with gpt-3.5-turbo.
chunk_content: Troubleshooting### How do I enable fine-tuning? Create a custom model is greyed out in Azure OpenAI Studio?In order to successfully access fine-tuning you need Cognitive Services OpenAI Contributor assigned. Even someone with high-level Service Administrator permissions would still need this account explicitly set in order to access fine-tuning. For more information please review the role-based access control guidance.
